<h1 style="margin-left: 4px; margin-top: -40px; margin-bottom: 30px;">Director Application Process</h1>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="background-color: #eef3f7; border-bottom: 3px solid #ddd;">
<p style="margin-left: 0px; font-size: 22px; color: #33302e; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 5px;">Directors</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="background-color: #f8f8f8; height: 250px; border-bottom: 3px solid #ddd;">
<p style="margin-left: 5px;">Student Support sponsors&nbsp;five student organizations known as councils. Each council (except SRC) is                       overseen by a student director who works with multiple coordinators and program managers. Each council oversees groups of student                       volunteers and/or members.</p>
<p><strong>Student Councils</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Get Connected Council</li>
<li>Involvement Council</li>
<li>Campus&nbsp;Ambassadors Council</li>
<li>Student Ambassadors Council</li>
<li>Student Associations Council</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="background-color: #f8f8f8;">
<p style="margin-top: 20px;">Directors are selected a semester in advance. Applications are due at the time of interviews.</p>
<p>Completed Applications include:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="#">Online Application</a></li>
<li>Written Essay - (1-2 pages) on why you want to be a director.&nbsp; Send to <a href="mailto:jonesa@byui.edu">jonesa@byui.edu</a>.</li>
<li>2 Letters of Reference (optional)</li>
<li>Leadership Resume (one page)</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-top: 5px;">Interviews will be held in November, February, and June. Please contact us for specific dates and times.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="background-color: #eef3f7; border-top: 3px solid #ddd;">
<p style="font-size: 12px; height: 12px; margin-top: 10px;">Have more questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:spiritevents@byui.edu">spiritevents@byui.edu</a></p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
